description.narrative: UNICEF developed and strengthened partnerships with decision makers, the private sector, donors and the media, increasing its sphere of influence for child rights related advocacy. During the year, the proportion of digital supporters of UNICEF social media accounts grew by 23% for Facebook and by 52% for Twitter, positioning UNICEF as a trusted and credible voice for children’s rights. More than two million users received messages on children’s rights via UNICEF social media accounts. The Regional Office acknowledged UNICEF for its contribution to ECAR social media accounts traffic, linked to the Kosovo related social media content provided. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:18/01/2022
